It is currently 100% occupied. Provided leases are month to month and leased as follows: Unit #1 is leased for $800, unit #2 is leased for $650, unit #3 is leased for $650, unit #4 is leased for $800, unit #5 is leased for $750 and unit #6 is leased for $800.
